402
00:26:06,785 --> 00:26:08,160
À vous, maintenant.

403
00:26:08,610 --> 00:26:10,334
<i>Enlevez ce miroir!</i>

404
00:26:10,626 --> 00:26:12,481
<i>- Ouvrez la bouche.
